---
title: Balsamic-Glazed Steak with Cheesy Garlic Bread and Arugula Salad
description: Juicy steaks are drizzled with a sweet and zesty balsamic glaze. Swipe the easy and cheesy pull-apart bread in the delicious pan juices. Arugula perks up the whole meal!
